5
1 Point and 2 Points (2)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par There are some people losing only by few points and they feel if they would have played here or there, they would have won easily.
\par
\par However the real pain is coming from the endgame.
\par
\par One might \cf1\b laugh\cf0\b0  because of \cf1\b 1 point\cf0\b0  and one might \cf1\b cry\cf0\b0  because of \cf1\b 1 point\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par Let's say there are only two endgame moves left, A and B.
\par
\par Which one is bigger?
\par }
