Dia. 01 If White Plays at 1
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If one wants to compare the value of the moves, he first has to decide how much each move is worth.
\par
\par What happens if White plays at 1?
\par White gets 1 point at A. Only White's territory has increased.
\par
\par
\par }
