Dia. 02 If Black Plays at 1
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Let's check what happens if Black plays at 1 this time.
\par In this case Black's territory hasn't increased.
\par
\par If we compare this with the previous diagram, the difference is either White's territory has increased by 1 or 0 point.
\par Therefore Black 1 in this diagram or (White 1 in \b Dia. 01\b0 ) is worth \cf1\b 1 point\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par }
