Dia. 04 If Black Plays at 1
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black plays at 1, White's territory hasn't decreased, but Black's territory has increased.
\par
\par Black's territory has changed at A and B. After White played, Black had no point at B anymore.
\par
\par Therefore Black 1 from this variation (White 1 from Dia. 03) is worth \cf1\b 2 points\cf0\b0 .
\par }
